  m_text: "The spacecraft confidently taps into the mighty forces of asteroid Psyche\u2014despite
    being millions of miles away. Maybe it's psychic? Maybe it's just wishful thinking?
    Either way, with a Massachusetts-sized metal asteroid as its imaginary power
    source, Psyche is feeling unstoppable."
